        "Description/Abstract": "We present our design exploration of reconfigurable Threshold Logic Gates (TLG) implemented using silver\u2013chalcogenide memristive devices combined with CMOS circuits. Results from simulations and physical circuits are shown. A variety of linearly separable logic functions including AND, OR, NAND, NOR have been realized in discrete hardware using a single-layer TLG. The functionality can be changed between these operations by reprogramming the resistance of the memristive devices.",
